#: ../cgi-bin/oppejoud.pl:299
msgid ""
"You can add a new name yourself. Just type the name into the search form and "
"press ｢SEARCH｣. You will see a button that will lead you to a page where you "
"will need to fill the required information (you only need first and last "
"names)."
msgstr ""
"Sina saad õppejõude ise lisada. Sisesta õppejõu nimi otsingu välja ja vajuta "
"｢OTSI｣. Siis näed nuppu, mis viib sind lehele, kus täidad vajalikku "
"informatsiooni (on vaja sisestada vaid õppejõu ees- ja perekonnanime)."

#: ../cgi-bin/oppejoud.pl:300
msgid ""
"If you have a long list of names, I'd be happy if you contributed it (either "
"in an automated way using the form mentioned above, or by simply"
msgstr ""
"Kui sul on pikk õppejõudude nimekiri, võid selle lisada ülalpool mainitud "
"vormi kaudu automaatselt (või lihtsalt"

#: ../cgi-bin/oppejoud.pl:300
msgid "sending the list to me"
msgstr "saata mulle"

#: ../cgi-bin/oppejoud.pl:301
msgid "Professors"
msgstr "Õppejõud"

#: ../cgi-bin/oppejoud.pl:302
msgid "I do not want others to write things about me!"
msgstr "Ma ei taha, et keegi kirjutaks minust!"

#: ../cgi-bin/oppejoud.pl:303
msgid "Why not? 😊"
msgstr "Miks mitte? 😊"

# perl-brace-format
#: ../cgi-bin/oppejoud.pl:304
#, fuzzy, perl-format, perl-brace-format
msgid ""
"Over {percent}% of feedbacks on this website are positive or neutral. If you "
"are a great professor (and I hope you are!), then there is nothing to worry "
"about."
msgstr ""
"Üle {percent}% kommentaaridest sellel veebilehel on positiivsed või "
"neutraalsed. Kui oled hea õppejõud (ma loodan, et oled!), siis ei ole "
"millestki muretseda."

#: ../cgi-bin/oppejoud.pl:305
msgid ""
"Somebody will always be unhappy, but that's OK. Consider it as an "
"opportunity to improve yourself, and as a result to have an even better "
"impact on our next generation of specialists!"
msgstr ""
"Keegi on alati õnnetu ja see on OK. Kaalutle seda nagu võimalust ennast "
"paremaks teha!"

#: ../cgi-bin/oppejoud.pl:306
msgid ""
"My university already has a system for feedbacks, I like it more than your "
"website"
msgstr ""
"Minu ülikoolis on juba olemas süsteem, kus saab kommentaare jätta ja see "
"meeldib mulle rohkem kui see portaal"

#: ../cgi-bin/oppejoud.pl:307
msgid ""
"Let's be honest here: how much do you care about feedbacks left in a non-"
"public system of your university (do you even read them?), and how much do "
"you care about things written on this website?"
msgstr ""
"Ütle ausalt, kui palju sa hoolid suletud süsteemis jäetud kommentaaridest? "
"Kas sa üldse loed neid? Ja palju sa hoolid sellest, mis on sellel veebilehel "
"kirjutatud?"

#: ../cgi-bin/oppejoud.pl:308
msgid ""
"If your university was publishing all of the feedbacks, your name wouldn't "
"be on this website."
msgstr ""
"Kui sinu ülikool oleks kõiki kommentaare avalikeks teinud, seda veebilehte "
"ei eksisteeriks."

#: ../cgi-bin/oppejoud.pl:309
msgid "Someone wrote lies about me!"
msgstr "Keegi kirjutas laimu minu kohta!"

#: ../cgi-bin/oppejoud.pl:310
msgid ""
"Feel free to leave a comment yourself to explain the situation. There have "
"been cases like this."
msgstr ""
"Jäta ise kommentaar ja seleta olukord lahti. Selliseid olukordi on juhtunud."

